Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪个人都拥有自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那愿望实现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是否能说自己是幸福的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他醒过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  总还是会到来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达下一个世界喽～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达什么到达！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这白色的家伙！就不能着陆得再正常点吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是侑子来的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元的魔女来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种文字我看不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色情人节的时候要加倍还来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是迟了就罚偿还三倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄件人  侑子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  瞪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有羽毛！摩可拿感觉到很强烈的羽毛的波动！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定会把羽毛拿到…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查过遗迹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知这里是远古时的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就在这里种花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要恢复它以前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  这件事可以告诉大家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上的人们也经常来这里玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想知道是谁种的这花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连哥哥都听到传言了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说要是找到了种花的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要让他继承王位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事能帮我保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有点兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道事情真相的只有我和小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  这是我们两人之间的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知怎么一下子就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为这一阵子都太努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身体先想睡一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑磷把小狼抱来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其道歉不如不要倒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是这个村子的长老哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我们抱着小狼走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对我们说「要不要来我家里」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在为了寻访不可思议的传说或事件而旅行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这个村子里也有这一类的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个空中神殿里供奉着支配着我们的神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里本来是在大地上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在半年前的一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是异变并不仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神下谕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神下了什么谕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「我可以实现某人任意的一个愿望」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么愿望都可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能得到这恩惠的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有第一个进入那神殿中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里的男丁们为了实现自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争先恐后地冲向神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大多数人都被保护神殿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑的军队袭击  失去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了现在  已经没有人想去神殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是不想死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就绝对不要靠近那座神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑～磷  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在思考什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有规定人不准思考的法律吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望吗？这个简单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本所在的地方  想要立刻回去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  黑大人要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己的愿望能实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要独自回到原来的世界去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追你的人绝对不会去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本所在的地方  不想要再回去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛应该就在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在…呼唤我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里有人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  沉睡着奔赴神殿而失去生命的人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我孙子的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听我的劝阻想要去神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变得冰冷的回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概羽毛就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是只为了羽毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就去见识见识「漆黑的军队」的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是小樱的羽毛  出发信号发出～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个自以为是的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱  腿不累么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到了什么东西的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好像有种不好的预感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个神殿里的神  说是什么愿望都能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他许愿说  要取回公主所有的记忆的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让他得逞  才会派遣我的兵士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这样看来没办法和他们讲理了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就放手大闹一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  快走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  法伊先生还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先走吧  我马上就会赶上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊先生  我马上去帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君你还有必须要做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去解决自己的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事就不必担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  就让我来做你们的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到有机会去那个人去不了的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在该怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能让法伊先生一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下脚步犹豫的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是输家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论从哪边上  都给我一起放马过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君  你看那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢先生！这些家伙只是来拖住我们脚步的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢先生！快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞪眼  是小樱的羽毛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么愿望我都能帮你们实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想请问一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这力量是原本就是属于你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勿庸置疑我能实现人们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但穿越次元时空的这片羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实给了我强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  神的力量也是源自公主的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  请快许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请公主许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却一个人得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君  我的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望  我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们两人的秘密哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  最后的愿望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然羽毛最后还是到了他们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到最差的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说是最好的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许马上就会苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奇迹啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是小樱的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑碰也是好人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「快走」的时候真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黑大大害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿·摩多基正兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那花儿…是谁种的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢电视前的大家一直以来的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼他们的旅程还会不断不断不断的继续
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在要和大家说再见了  真是舍不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有点寂寞的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.51,0:24:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过侑子不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.55,0:24:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切邂逅都是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相信以后还会在哪里和大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  要为那天来临而期待不已
